OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,FPeople are invited to use the newly
OL,7,Finstalled 'Letters to Heaven' postbox
OL,8,Fin Penrith as a source of comfort
OL,9,Fafter losing a loved one.
OL,11,FLaunched in time for Father's Day on
OL,12,FSunday, the post box will be a
OL,13,Fpermanent feature at the town's
OL,14,Fcemetery in Beacon Edge.
OL,16,FWestmorland and Furness councillor
OL,17,FJohn Murray said he hopes this will
OL,18,Fbring "a little extra solace to
OL,19,Ffamilies and friends who are mourning
OL,20,Floved ones."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
