FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782389902
OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,F"Everybody is welcome to post their
OL,7,Fcards and letters into the box in a
OL,8,Fsealed envelope, at any time, and
OL,9,Fthese will be treated with the
OL,10,Fgreatest respect by our team," he
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,F"No address or stamp is needed as the
OL,14,Fpost box is not linked to the Royal
OL,15,FMail, and the envelopes will not be
OL,16,Fopened or read."
OL,18,FThe idea came from Richardsons Funeral
OL,19,FDirectors, based in Penrith, and was
OL,20,Finspired by a nationwide Letters to
OL,21,FHeaven project.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
