PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782389902
OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,FRichardsons have donated the post box,
OL,7,Fwhich has been installed by
OL,8,FWestmorland and Furness Council and
OL,9,Fcan be used by anybody regardless of
OL,10,Fwhere their loved one lived or their
OL,11,Ffuneral took place.
OL,13,FThe contents will remain completely
OL,14,Fconfidential and will be carefully
OL,15,Fmanaged by colleagues from the
OL,16,Fcouncil's Bereavement Services.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
