FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782389902
OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,F"I first heard about Letters to Heaven
OL,7,Fpost boxes when we sadly lost my son-
OL,8,Fin-law last year," explained Sue
OL,9,FEmmerson, of Richardsons Funeral
OL,10,FDirectors.
OL,12,F"My daughter Suzanne and grandchildren
OL,13,FMaisy and Freddy found it very
OL,14,Fcomforting to remember Kev on special
OL,15,Foccasions by visiting the Letters to
OL,16,FHeaven post box in Keswick, and I hope
OL,17,Fthat lots of families will be helped
OL,18,Fby having a similar post box in
OL,19,FPenrith as a focal point for posting
OL,20,Ftheir memories.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
