OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1782389902
OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,F"Everyone at Richardsons is very
OL,7,Fpleased that the post box we are
OL,8,Fdonating will be located at Penrith
OL,9,FCemetery, and we're grateful to the
OL,10,Fcouncil for taking on the continued
OL,11,Fcare of the Letters to Heaven post box.
OL,13,F"We hope the simple act of putting pen
OL,14,Fto paper will help people express
OL,15,Ftheir emotions and feel connected to
OL,16,Ftheir loved ones as they grieve."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
