OL,3,C'Letters to heaven' postbox aims to
OL,4,Cbring comfort to people grieving
OL,6,FCouncillor Murray added, "The letters
OL,7,Fwill never leave Penrith Cemetery as
OL,8,Fthey will be shredded and composted to
OL,9,Fhelp enhance the beautiful grounds for
OL,10,Feveryone to appreciate."
